data.description: This lovely 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom home is situated on a cul-de-sac lot.  Primary bedroom complete with an en-suite bathroom featuring dual vanities, walk in shower shower and an oversized tub. The beautiful kitchen offers ample storage and counter space, with a breakfast bar overlooking the expansive living room and a designated dining area. Enjoy the generously sized and welcoming living room, providing ample space for relaxation and hosting gatherings! Bonus room just off of the kitchen can be used for a home office, fitness room, reading room or kids playroom. The possibilities are endless. But wait! There's more to it – this residence is situated within a community that provides a variety of amenities. Enjoy the community swimming pool, discover the beauty of nature in the two nearby parks, or join fellow residents for a delightful BBQ. Solar Panels Pay at Closing
